      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean i'm at fault for still being here? i just mean i can't see a path forward. the money is gone, the people i hired are out of work, and everyone i know thinks i'm a joke. it feels like the only way to stop the world from looking at me like this is to just... not be present for it anymore. like the shame is just too much to carry.",
